<subSubSection pageId="2" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="2.[151,1437,1289,1782]" pageId="2">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,1685,1710]" pageId="2">Remarks.</emphasis>
This is the first record for Cephalonia. The status of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Tamanini. Apterous" authorityYear="1971" box="[908,1050,1685,1709]" class="Insecta" family="Veliidae" genus="Velia" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="2" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="mariae">
<emphasis box="[908,1050,1685,1709]" italics="true" pageId="2">Velia mariae</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, previously misidentified with the Cretan endemic 
<emphasis box="[334,533,1721,1745]" italics="true" pageId="2">V. r. rhadamantha</emphasis>
Hoberlandt, 1941, has recently been clarified by 
<bibRefCitation author="Csabai, Z. &amp; Soos, N. &amp; Berchi, G. M. &amp; Cianferoni, F. &amp; Boda, P. &amp; Mora, A." box="[1087,1307,1721,1746]" pageId="2" pagination="51 - 69" refId="ref8620" refString="Csabai, Z., Soos, N., Berchi, G. M., Cianferoni, F., Boda, P. &amp; Mora, A. (2017) Aquatic and semiaquatic Heteroptera (Nepomorpha and Gerromorpha) fauna of Greek holiday islands (Rhodes, Crete and Corfu) with first records of three species from Europe and Greece. Zootaxa, 4231 (1), 51 - 69. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 4231.1.3" type="journal article" year="2017">
Csabai 
<emphasis box="[1170,1226,1721,1745]" italics="true" pageId="2">et al.</emphasis>
(2017)
</bibRefCitation>
and 
<bibRefCitation author="Berchi, G. M. &amp; Copilas &amp; Ciocianu, D. &amp; Kment, P. &amp; Buzzetti, F. M. &amp; Petrusek, A. &amp; Rakosy, I. &amp; Cianferoni, F. &amp; Damgaard, J." pageId="2" pagination="262 - 276" refId="ref8004" refString="Berchi, G. M., Copilas? Ciocianu, D., Kment, P., Buzzetti, F. M., Petrusek, A., Rakosy, I., Cianferoni, F. &amp; Damgaard, J. (2018 b) Molecular phylogeny and biogeography of the West? Palaearctic Velia (Heteroptera: Gerromorpha: Veliidae). Systematic Entomology, 43 (2), 262 - 276. [first published online: 17 October 2017] https: // doi. org / 10.1111 / syen. 12273" type="journal article" year="2018">
Berchi 
<emphasis box="[151,207,1757,1781]" italics="true" pageId="2">et al.</emphasis>
(2018b)
</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
